{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build a Shopify custom section called “Upcoming Retreats – Spotlight Scroll”.
    
    Design:
    - Same header as screenshot: eyebrow “JOIN US”, heading “Upcoming Retreats”, subtitle below.
    - Stacked list of retreat cards (blocks), image left and content right on desktop, stacked on mobile.
    - Same content fields: location, dates, title, description, 3 tags, price, duration, spots left, apply button.
    
    Animation concept (animate everything + change it up):
    - Entrance (once):
      - Header fades/masks in (eyebrow → heading → subtitle).
      - All cards fade in softly with a slight rise (8px).
    - Scroll spotlight behavior (continuous, subtle):
      - As the user scrolls, the card that is most centered in the viewport gets an “active” state:
        - active card: scale 1.00, stronger shadow, full opacity
        - inactive cards: scale 0.985, slightly reduced opacity (still readable)
      - Image inside active card gets tiny parallax drift (translateY small amount) for depth.
      - Tags on the active card brighten slightly.
    
    Implementation:
    - Use IntersectionObserver with threshold ~0.55 to toggle an “is-active” class per card.
    - Use requestAnimationFrame for optional parallax (very small range).
    - Disable spotlight + parallax on mobile and prefers-reduced-motion.
    - No external libraries. Include schema for colors + animation toggles.
    
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-retreat-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: {{ block.settings.eyebrow_color }};
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(8px);
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-eyebrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}.is-visible {
    animation: ai-retreat-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(8px);
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}.is-visible {
    animation: ai-retreat-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 0.8s ease-out 0.15s forwards;
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(8px);
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}.is-visible {
    animation: ai-retreat-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 0.8s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
  }

  @keyframes ai-retreat-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .ai-retreat-spotlight-list-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-retreat-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 40px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(8px);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
                box-shadow 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
                opacity 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    will-change: transform, box-shadow, opacity;
  }

  .ai-retreat-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.is-loaded {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .ai-retreat-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.is-active {
    transform: scale(1.00);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .ai-retreat-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:not(.is-active) {
    transform: scale(0.985);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .ai-retreat-card-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    min-height: 400px;
  }

